bjf 

This is small utility to display all neccessary informations of the file in one place.

Utility shows in file section:

1) filename
2) size in bytes
3) block size
4) number of allocated blocks
5) inode number
6) number of hard links
7) device id
9) time of last access
10) time of last modification
11) time of last change

and in user section:

12) UID and GID of the owner
13) name of the owner and name of the group
14) gecos field
15) home folder path
16) user shell




